            <text font-size="medium">TownCode inconsistent with Reason for Reporting(01)</text>
            <spacer height="15" />
          </line>
          <line border="none">
            <cell border="none" cell-span="1" line-span="1">
              <spacer width="15" />
              <text font-size="medium">If Reason for Reporting (DOE011) = 01 (resident) - then the Town of Residence code (DOE014) must be a member town of the district (except for students receiving sped services).</text>
            </cell>
          </line>
        </block>
      </row>
      <row>
