          </line>
          <line border="none">
            <cell border="none" cell-span="1" line-span="1">
              <spacer width="15" />
              <text font-size="medium">1. Verify that the town code is populated and has a valid state code.</text>
            </cell>
          </line>
          <line border="none">
            <cell border="none" cell-span="1" line-span="1">
              <spacer width="15" />
              <text font-size="medium">2. Verify that the town code that is populated is a member town of the district.</text>
            </cell>
          </line>
          <line border="none">
            <cell border="none" cell-span="1" line-span="1">
              <spacer width="15" />
              <text font-size="medium">3. Verify the values in Aspen match the values shown in the DESE error code.</text>
            </cell>
          </line>
          <line border="none">
            <cell border="none" cell-span="1" line-span="1">
              <spacer width="15" />
              <text font-size="medium">4. If the above varies, re-publish StudentPersonal and StudentSchoolEnrollment topics (District View &gt; Tools &gt; Procedures, SIF Publish SELECT Student Objects)</text>
